Trainz pre-compiled asset Libraries, *.JA files can be uploaded into the next generation Trainz in most cases, and with some limitations. In point of fact, cross loading assets sometimes runs afoul of a incompatibility of scripts in *.gs files when doing so, and correcting these issues can be vexing, as where what changed, and which asset needs which change to work with the newer more modern *.gs files is not always immediately obvious. It takes a little sleuthing and trial and error, advice seeking on the forums, and is just a bother when an older asset runs afoul of a new system.

To be continued from that start
