==Order Schizaeales==

The order '''{{fny-w|Schizaeales}}''' contains the seemingly dissimilar curly-grass and climbing ferns.

===Family Lygodiaceae===

The {{fny-w|Lygodiaceae}} (climbing-fern family) consists of the single genus ''{{fny-w|Lygodium}}'', which in New York, is represented by the endangered American climbing fern.

