==Dealing with Asset Errors==
'''Errors, Faults, Faulty assets, Bad Content, Faulty content'' are all synonyms in Trainz-speak for the same situation: An asset has become or was distributed with malformed components. Another kind of error or fault occurs when the asset needs an tweak to conform to a newer level of asset technology. The flaw is frequently something which can be 'fixed' by hand edited changes into the files in the assets defining folder(s) opened in the  operating system. 

